Exiftool- ExifTool is a powerful, free, and open-source command-line application used for reading, writing, and 
editing meta information in a wide variety of files (mostly images, but also audio, video, and PDFs).
Ex:If you've ever wanted to look under the hood of a digital photo to see exactly when it was taken, what camera was used, or where the GPS coordinates point, ExifTool is the gold standard tool for the job.

